  "slug": "reach-behind",
  "title": "Reach Behind",
  "description": "Click through decorations and interact with the blocks behind them.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Twitter&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=x&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"116\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@heyitsfuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Reach Behind</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> lets you interact with usable blocks hidden behind decorations such as item frames, signs, banners, and other supported attachments. Open a chest, use a crafting table, or access other blocks without needing to aim around the decorations you've placed. 🖱️</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The mod makes decorated builds more practical by removing a common source of frustration while preserving normal decoration interactions. An optional empty hand mode helps prevent accidental edits, item placement, and other unwanted interactions. 🧰</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It works in singleplayer, on dedicated servers, and even in multiplayer when the server does not have the mod installed. For the most complete and consistent experience, install the mod on both client and server. 🌐</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🖼️ Click Through Decorations:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Interact with usable blocks behind item frames, glow item frames, signs, and banners.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">📦 Easier Hidden Storage:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Open attached containers like chests without needing to click around decorative blocks or entities.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🛠️ Works With Functional Blocks:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Use chests, crafting tables and other interactive blocks even when covered by supported decorations.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌐 Flexible Client and Server Use:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Works in singleplayer, server-side multiplayer, and client-only multiplayer with server-side limitations.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🤝 Best With Both Sides Installed:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> When installed on both client and server, interactions are handled consistently for all players.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">✋ Empty-Hand Safety Option:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Optionally require an empty hand to help preserve normal decoration interactions such as applying items to signs.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⚙️ Customisable Support Lists:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Configure which attached blocks and entities allow clicks to pass through.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🔌 Modded Compatibility Hooks:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Includes support for compatible mods, such as </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fast-item-frames\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Fast Item Frames</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, when present.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/media/1.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INSTALLATION OPTIONAL ON CLIENT &amp; OPTIONAL ON SERVER</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/puzzles-lib\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PUZZLES LIB</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC &amp; NEOFORGE)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FABRIC API</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FORGE CONFIG API PORT</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/configuration.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If available for a mod, configuration is possible directly from in-game using the mod menu (requires </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod Menu</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> by </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Prospector\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Prospector</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> to be installed on Fabric).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For manual configuration using an external text editor all files are found at </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.minecraft/config</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, named as </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-client.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-common.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, or </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-server.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, depending on the type of config. Not all types might exist for a mod, if any at all.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/easy-anvils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/easy-magic\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easymagic/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/open-together\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/studio.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/reachbehind/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n",
